          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV",
                "EXTB",
                "GSPEC",
                "TTM",
                "STTA",
                "EDEG"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Thick-target yields",
                "of the natZr(p,x)90Nb reaction were measured. For the",
                "irradiation, stacked targets were prepared, each",
                "consisting of three Zr disks of 0.25mm thickness and",
                "a 0.5 mm thick Al cover foil. The initial proton beam",
                "energy was set to 20 MeV, which was then decreased to",
                "17.5 MeV by the Al cover foil. Each stacked target",
                "was irradiated for 1 hour with an average beam",
                "current of 5 uA. The production yield was determined",
                "based by gamma ray spectroscopy, 24 hours after EOB.",
                "The reported value is the mean of three irradiations."
              ]
            }
          ],
